SELECT * FROM main_marts.dim_admission_sources","cellId":3,"useDatabase":"ducklake"},{"query":"-- Show me patients that got transfered to treatment due to Court/Law Enforcement

SELECT 
  visit.age as age_group,
  COUNT(visit.age) as age_count,
  ROUND(
    COUNT(visit.age) * 100.0 / SUM(COUNT(visit.age)) OVER (),
    2
  ) AS age_group_percentage
FROM
  main_marts.fact_patient_visits visit
  LEFT JOIN main_marts.dim_admission_sources adm_source
    ON visit.admission_source_id = adm_source.admission_source_id

WHERE adm_source.description = 'Court/Law Enforcement'
GROUP BY visit.age
